fast-cdr
------------------------------------------
eProsima Fast CDR is a C++ library that provides two serialization mechanisms.
One is the standard CDR serialization mechanism, while the other is a faster
implementation that modifies the standard.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libfastcdr-devel-2.3.6-1bl1
  libfastcdr2-2.3.6-1bl1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  make-4.4.1-2
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/eProsima/Fast-CDR

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/eProsima/Fast-CDR/archive/refs/tags/v2.3.6.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack fast-cdr-2.3.6-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./fast-cdr-2.3.6-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/fast-cdr-2.3.6-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/fast-cdr-2.3.6-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libfastcdr2-2.3.6-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libfastcdr-devel-2.3.6-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

